      "summary": "BullMQ consumer for the publish queue that uploads a Comparison's completed render to YouTube via the Data API v3, honoring Upload.scheduledAt for future-dated releases and setting an A/B thumbnail variant; safely retried since it no-ops if the Upload already has a videoId.",
