      "name": "render-worker.ts",
      "filePath": "apps/workers/src/workers/render-worker.ts",
      "summary": "BullMQ consumer for the render queue that renders a Comparison's frozen videoJson through either a local @remotion/renderer bundle or Remotion Lambda (depending on RENDER_TARGET), produces A/B thumbnail variants, tracks progress in RenderJob, and enqueues the follow-up publish job.",
