      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "renderLocally() and renderOnLambda() implement the same RenderResult contract via two very different mechanisms (in-process renderMedia vs. polling getRenderProgress), letting processRenderJob() branch on isLambdaRenderTarget() without leaking Lambda details elsewhere."
